notes: Manually curated BACnet point catalog for Flexit Nordic units.
This catalog intentionally excludes source/provenance metadata.
Point details come from BACnet spreadsheet export fields; notes capture learned Flexit GO behavior.
Example values are anonymized representative values.

learnedBehaviorNotes.note: Flexit GO sends writeProperty presentValue=0 (priority 16) when replacing filters, even though documentation marks the point as read-only.
Flexit GO shows filter interval in months (3..12), but writes/reads this point in hours.
Flexit GO additional-heating menu reads presentValue and proprietary property 5093; observed writes use priority 13.
Flexit GO additional-heating menu reads this point as heating neutral-zone value for HOME mode.
Flexit GO additional-heating menu reads this point as heating neutral-zone value for AWAY mode.
